OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain becoming widespread this evening,
OL,7,Fmostly light but with some heavier
OL,8,Fbursts possible. By dawn, outbreaks of
OL,9,Fmainly light rain are likely to turn
OL,10,Fmore intermittent. Winds easing.
OL,11,FRemaining mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FOutbreaks of mostly light rain
OL,14,Fand drizzle easing through the
OL,15,Fmorning, before turning heavier again
OL,16,Ftowards the north in the afternoon and
OL,17,Fevening, and moving south. Light
OL,18,Fwinds. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
