OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith rain Saturday morning, gradually
OL,7,Fturning brighter. Winds strengthening
OL,8,FSunday, but otherwise similar with
OL,9,Fearly rain easing to brighter spells.
OL,10,FBreezy Monday but drier with variable
OL,11,Fcloud. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
